    Class and Description
    BulletFoodController
    Controls all ammo (bullet food)
    ConstrainedToArea
    Interface for things within areas such as canvas bounds, etc.
    ContainsObject
    Things that contain objects on a canvas there is an optional inner object for things with 2 items
    Direction
    Enum of directions (including shoot for Snake's keybinding mechanism)
    FoodController
    Controls all food
    Grid
    Draws a grid on the canvas in the background
    Instructions
    Class which displays instructions for playing the game
    KeyController
    Controls and forwards keystrokes
    KeyHandler
    interface for objects that should recieve keypresses
    Moveable
    abstract class - contains direction specific methods from an extension of ContainsObject
    ObjectController
    Abstract superclass for all controllers of objects (obstacles)
    Removable
    Things that can be destroyed - recommended for removeFromCanvas, etc Formerly called Destroyable, but conflicted with an existing interface
    ScoreBoard
    scoreboard for the game, tracks snake's ammo and length
    Snake

    SnakePiece

    SplitterController
    Controls all splitters
    Teleport
    Teleporter
    TeleportController
    Controls all teleporters
    Tickable
    Tickable object interface - all items should do something on each "tick"
    World
    Main thread of the program executes here through ActiveObject
    WorldController
    Controls the world
